cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation, which is a subfield of natural language processing. The use of a recursive neural network also suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the use of neural networks for feature learning could also place it in the sub-category cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the mention of experiments suggests that it could also belong to the sub-category cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), although this is less likely than the other sub-categories mentioned.
